Oh absolutely.  The fault does not lie with the Monks for wanting the armor or using the armor.  The mistake is clearly Verant's for making it available.  You point out how bad the other Velious armor is for Monks, yet it is consistant with what was made available previously (frankly I think they should have beefed it up just a tad but not to the point of competing with plate melee AC).<br>
